Visualization¶

Visualizing number of crimes took place in each district from 2010 to 2019¶

In [28]:
f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(6, 6))
sns.set_color_codes("muted")
sns.barplot(data=pandas_areas,x="AREA NAME",y='count',color='b')
plt.title('Number of crimes in each Area of LA')
plt.subplots_adjust(right=3)
ax.set(ylim=(70000, 150000))
sns.despine(left=True, bottom=True)
plt.show()

This gragh shows total number of crimes took place in each district from 2010-2019. Through this we can observe that the top three major crime ridden areas in LA are:

  1. 77th Street
  2. Southwest
  3. N Hollywood
